<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>StoreWise — Staff Quick Guide</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

:root {
  --teal:  #1a8c9c;
  --teal-lt: #e6f7f9;
  --gold:  #e8a020;
  --gold-lt: #fef7e8;
  --red:   #c0152f;
  --red-lt: #fce8e8;
  --green: #1a7a4a;
  --green-lt: #e8f8f0;
  --ink:   #0d1f23;
  --ink-60: #5a7178;
  --ink-20: #dde6e8;
  --bg:    #f8fbfc;
  --white: #ffffff;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding: 0;
}

/* ── TOP BAR ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.topbar {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: white;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 14px 32px;
}

.topbar-logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 16px;
}

.topbar-logo span { font-size: 22px; }

.topbar-links { display: flex; gap: 16px; }

.topbar-links a {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.topbar-links a:hover { color: white; }

.print-btn {
  background: var(--teal);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  padding: 8px 18px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.print-btn:hover { background: #0f5c68; }

/* ── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.page-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, #0f5c68 100%);
  color: white;
  padding: 48px 32px 40px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.page-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 32px 32px;
}

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  color: white;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 5px 14px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  position: relative;
}

.page-hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  position: relative;
}

.page-hero p {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  font-weight: 300;
  position: relative;
}

/* ── CONTENT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.content {
  max-width: 960px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 32px 80px;
}

/* ── SECTION ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.guide-section {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.guide-section-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

.guide-section-title .section-num {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  background: var(--teal);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── STEPS FLOW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.steps-flow {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
}

.step-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 18px 16px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}

.step-card::after {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute;
  right: -12px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  color: var(--ink-60);
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  z-index: 1;
}

.step-card:last-child::after { display: none; }

.step-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.step-label { font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.step-sub   { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-60); font-weight: 300; }

/* ── TWO COLUMN ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }

/* ── CARD ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card-header {
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--ink);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.card-body { padding: 16px 18px; }

/* ── CHECKLIST ROW ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.checklist-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 8px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
  font-size: 13px;
}

.checklist-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.row-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.dot-green  { background: var(--green); }
.dot-gold   { background: var(--gold); }
.dot-red    { background: var(--red); }
.dot-teal   { background: var(--teal); }

.row-text { flex: 1; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; }
.row-text strong { font-weight: 600; }

/* ── SHORTCUT TABLE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.shortcut-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 13px;
}

.shortcut-table th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink-60);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 11px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
}

.shortcut-table td {
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-20);
  color: var(--ink);
  vertical-align: top;
}

.shortcut-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

kbd {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: white;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: monospace;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ── ALERT BOX ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.alert-box {
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  font-size: 13px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.alert-box.green { background: var(--green-lt); color: #0f4a2c; border: 1px solid rgba(26,122,74,0.2); }
.alert-box.gold  { background: var(--gold-lt);  color: #7a5000; border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,32,0.25); }
.alert-box.red   { background: var(--red-lt);   color: #7a0a1a; border: 1px solid rgba(192,21,47,0.2); }

/* ── EMERGENCY BOX ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.emergency {
  background: var(--red-lt);
  border: 2px solid var(--red);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
}

.emergency-title {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--red);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.emergency-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.emergency-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.emergency-num {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  background: var(--red);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

/* ── FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.footer {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 28px 32px;
  font-size: 12px;
}
.footer a { color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }
.footer strong { color: white; }

/* ── PRINT STYLES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media print {
  .topbar, .print-btn { display: none !important; }
  .page-hero { background: var(--teal) !important; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; }
  .step-card, .card { break-inside: avoid; }
  body { background: white; }
  .content { padding: 20px; }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .steps-flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .step-card::after { display: none; }
  .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .content { padding: 24px 16px 60px; }
  .topbar { padding: 12px 16px; }
  .page-hero { padding: 36px 16px 28px; }
  .topbar-links { display: none; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-logo"><span>🏪</span> StoreWise AI</div>
  <div class="topbar-links">
    <a href="index.html">Open App</a>
    <a href="training.html">Full Training</a>
  </div>
  <button class="print-btn" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Print</button>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">👤 Staff Reference</div>
  <h1>Staff Quick Guide</h1>
  <p>Everything you need to process sales and manage your shift — keep this page open or print it out.</p>
</div>

<!-- CONTENT -->
<div class="content">

  <!-- SECTION 1: HOW TO PROCESS A SALE -->
  <div class="guide-section">
    <div class="guide-section-title">
      <div class="section-num">1</div>
      How to Process a Sale
    </div>
    <div class="steps-flow">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">🔑</div>
        <div class="step-label">Unlock the App</div>
        <div class="step-sub">Enter your PIN on the lock screen</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">💳</div>
        <div class="step-label">Open Sales & POS</div>
        <div class="step-sub">Click "Sales & POS" in the sidebar</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">🛒</div>
        <div class="step-label">Add Products</div>
        <div class="step-sub">Search by name or scan barcode</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">✅</div>
        <div class="step-label">Process Payment</div>
        <div class="step-sub">Click "Process Payment" and select cash or card</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="alert-box green" style="margin-top:16px;">
      ✅ Stock levels update <strong>automatically</strong> when a sale is completed. You don't need to do anything extra.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 2: COMMON TASKS -->
  <div class="guide-section">
    <div class="guide-section-title"><div class="section-num">2</div>Common Tasks</div>
    <div class="two-col">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">🛒 Managing the Cart</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Add item:</strong> Type name in search bar — it adds automatically when found</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Change quantity:</strong> Use <kbd>+</kbd> and <kbd>-</kbd> buttons next to each item</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Remove item:</strong> Click the <kbd>×</kbd> button next to the item</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-gold"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Clear cart:</strong> Click "Clear Cart" to start over — this does NOT complete a sale</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">💰 Payment Types</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-green"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Cash:</strong> Select "Cash" on the payment screen. The system records it as cash — you handle change manually.</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-green"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Card:</strong> Select "Card" on the payment screen. Run the card through your card terminal separately.</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Customer name:</strong> Optional. Enter it on the payment screen for records.</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">🔍 Finding Products</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text">Type part of the product name in the search bar — it finds as you type</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text">Scan a barcode — the product is added to cart instantly</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-gold"></div><div class="row-text">If a product isn't found, contact your manager — it may need to be added to inventory</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">🔒 Locking the App</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text">Click <strong>🔒 Lock App</strong> in the sidebar footer before leaving the register</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-teal"></div><div class="row-text">The app auto-locks after 15 minutes of inactivity</div></div>
          <div class="checklist-row"><div class="row-dot dot-red"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Never leave the app unlocked</strong> when stepping away from the register</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 3: WHAT TO DO IF... -->
  <div class="guide-section">
    <div class="guide-section-title"><div class="section-num">3</div>What To Do If…</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body" style="padding:0;">
        <table class="shortcut-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Situation</th><th>What to do</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Product not found in search</td>
              <td>Try searching with fewer letters. If still not found, note the product and contact your manager to add it to inventory.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Wrong item added to cart</td>
              <td>Click the <kbd>×</kbd> button next to the item to remove it, or use <kbd>-</kbd> to reduce quantity to 0 is not possible — just remove it.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Completed a sale by mistake</td>
              <td>Contact your manager. The manager can check the transaction in Recent Transactions, but cannot reverse it in the app — they'll need to handle it manually.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>App shows "locked" screen</td>
              <td>Enter the store PIN. If you don't know it, contact your manager.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>App is blank / not loading</td>
              <td>Refresh the page. If it still doesn't load, check your internet connection and try again.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Customer wants a refund</td>
              <td>Handle the cash/card refund manually. Tell your manager so they can update inventory stock manually if needed.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Browser closes mid-sale</td>
              <td>Reopen the app and re-enter PIN. The cart is not saved between sessions — you'll need to re-add the items.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 4: WHAT NOT TO DO -->
  <div class="guide-section">
    <div class="guide-section-title"><div class="section-num">4</div>Important Rules</div>
    <div class="two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--red-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Don't delete products</strong> — only managers should do this</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--red-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Don't edit product prices</strong> without manager approval</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--red-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Don't share the PIN</strong> with customers or visitors</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--red-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-red" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Don't click Export/Import/Reset</strong> in Settings — those are manager functions</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--green-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-green" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Always complete a payment</strong> before clearing the cart</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--green-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-green" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Lock the app</strong> whenever you step away</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--green-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-green" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Tell your manager</strong> if stock looks wrong for any product</div></div>
        <div class="checklist-row" style="border:none;background:var(--green-lt);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;"><div class="row-dot dot-green" style="margin-top:5px;"></div><div class="row-text"><strong>Note the transaction ID</strong> shown after each completed sale</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- EMERGENCY -->
  <div class="emergency">
    <div class="emergency-title">🚨 If Something Goes Seriously Wrong</div>
    <div class="emergency-row"><div class="emergency-num">1</div><div>Don't click anything else — take a photo of the screen with your phone</div></div>
    <div class="emergency-row"><div class="emergency-num">2</div><div>Write down the last transaction ID and the time it happened</div></div>
    <div class="emergency-row"><div class="emergency-num">3</div><div>Call your manager immediately — don't try to fix it yourself</div></div>
    <div class="emergency-row"><div class="emergency-num">4</div><div>If the app is frozen, refresh the page — data is saved automatically</div></div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
  <p><strong>StoreWise AI</strong> · Staff Quick Guide · <a href="training.html">Full Training →</a> · <a href="index.html">Open App →</a></p>
  <p style="margin-top:6px;">Print this page and keep it at the register · Press Ctrl+P (or ⌘+P on Mac) to print</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
